p-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>11</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Southwest City Dog Park (Members Only)</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.5</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>St. Johns Community Dog Park</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.5</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Treecourt Unleashed Dog Adventure Park | Dog Park | (Registration Required)</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.4</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->St. Louis</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your St. Louis dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->St. Louis</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->St. Louis</h3><p>11<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.0<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">11</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/forest-park-southeast-members-only-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Forest Park Southeast Members Only Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Forest Park Southeast Members Only Dog Park provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of St. Louis.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Visitors appreciate the clean environment and friendly atmosphere, reflected in its 4.1-star rating. For more details, you can visit the [official website](https://www.stlouis-mo.gov/parks/parks/browse-parks/amenity.cfm?id=504) or check out local guides at [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/frenchtown-member-s-only-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Frenchtown Member&#x27;s Only Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">If you&#x27;re in St. Louis, bring your furry friend to Frenchtown Member&#x27;s Only Dog Park for a great day out.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Locals enjoy the convenient location and the opportunity for their dogs to burn off energy. Make sure to check the [official page](http://www.frenchtowndogpark.com/xxxx) for membership info. For more dog-friendly spots, browse [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/laclede-s-landing-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Laclede&#x27;s Landing Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Laclede&#x27;s Landing Dog Park provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of St. Louis.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Locals enjoy the convenient location and the opportunity for their dogs to burn off energy. Make sure to check the [official page](https://www.lacledeslanding.com/) for membership info. For more dog-friendly spots, browse [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/lucas-dog-park-membership-only\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Lucas Dog Park (membership only)</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Lucas Dog Park (membership only) provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of St. Louis.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Locals enjoy the convenient location and the opportunity for their dogs to burn off energy. For more details, you can visit the [official website](http://www.lucasparkdogpark.org/) or check out local guides at [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/shaw-dog-park-membership-only\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Shaw Dog Park (Membership Only)</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 10:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">If you&#x27;re in St. Louis, bring your furry friend to Shaw Dog Park (Membership Only) for a great day out.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Visitors appreciate the clean environment and friendly atmosphere, reflected in its 4.2-star rating. Plan your visit today! For rules and hours, see the [park website](http://shawstlouis.org/attractions-amenities/shaw-dog-park/) or verify details on [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/slu-dog-park-sculpture-garden\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">SLU Dog Park &amp; Sculpture Garden</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">SLU Dog Park &amp; Sculpture Garden provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of St. Louis.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Locals enjoy the convenient location and the opportunity for their dogs to burn off energy. For more details, you can visit the [official website](#) or check out local guides at [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/southwest-city-dog-park-members-only\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Southwest City Dog Park (Members Only)</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 10:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Located in St. Louis, Southwest City Dog Park (Members Only) offers a welcoming space for pets to exercise and socialize.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. With a solid 4.5-star rating from over 170 reviews, it&#x27;s a highly recommended community favorite. Plan your visit today! For rules and hours, see the [park website](https://swcitydogpark.org/) or verify details on [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/st-johns-community-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">St. Johns Community Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:30 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>St. Louis<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">St. Johns Community Dog Park provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of St. Louis.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. Visitors appreciate the clean environment and friendly atmosphere, reflected in its 4.5-star rating. Make sure to check the [official page](http://stjucc.org/) for membership info. For more dog-friendly spots, browse [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a></div><div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:2rem\"><button class=\"hero-cta primary\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;cursor:pointer\"><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down\"></i>Show More (<!-- -->3<!-- --> more)</button></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!-- -->St. Louis</h2><p>Worth the drive? Check out top-rated indoor parks in neighboring cities.</p></div><div class=\"nearby-cities-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem\"><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/kansas-city\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in Kansas City, MO\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/kansas-city/hero.webp\"/></div><div class=\"nearby-city-content\" style=\"padding:1rem\"><h3 style=\"font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:#0f172a\">Kansas City</h3><p style=\"font-size:0.875rem;color:#64748b\">8<!-- --> parks · <!-- -->4.3<!-- --> avg rating</p></div></a><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/columbia-mo\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in Columbia, MO\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=